===Conjunction===
{{en-con}}

# Despite the fact that; [[although]].
#: '''''Though''' it’s risky, it’s worth taking the chance.''
# {{context|archaic|lang=en}} [[if|If]], [[that]], [[even if]].
#: ''We shall be not sorry '''though''' the man die tonight.''
